Sentencas: To increase the cell performance of solid oxide fuel cells operated at intermediate temperature (600-800 degrees C), Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 (GDC) was applied to the La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF) cathode in electrode microstructure using sol-gel coating.
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: We employed a GDC as a diffusion barrier layer on the yttria-stabilized zironia (YSZ) electrolyte to prevent the interlayer formation of SrZrO3, which has poor ionic conductivity.
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This interfacial reaction product was hardly formed at the electrolyte-cathode interlayer after sintering the GDC layer resulting to reduce the cathode polarization resistance.
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, we use sol-gel method to coat GDC thin layer through the cathode pore wall surface to extend the triple phase boundary (TPB) area.
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathode polarization resistance also reduced due to the additional TPB area.
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For the single cell featuring LSCF cathode modified with GDC sol-gel coating, the maximum densities were 0.41 W/cm(2) and 0.89 W/cm(2) at 700 degrees C and 800 degrees C. (C) 2011
Titulo: Ce0.8Gd0.2O2 modification on La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 cathode for improving a cell performance in intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
